cs.NE, cs.ET, cs.AR, cs.EM, cs.CE 

This paper is about a bi-directional address event transceiver block for inter-chip communication in neuromorphic systems. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Other likely categories include cs.ET (Embedded Systems), cs.AR (Hardware Architecture), cs.EM (Electromagnetics), and cs.CE (Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science).
